    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.36.15aa" />
                
            <opener>
                <dateline>Skyrim, 5-4-'62</dateline>
                
                
                
                <salute>Dear Stewart:</salute>
            </opener>
                <p>Connie tells me that you are now fourteen years old, and I believe her. So I am sending the wherewithal for a modest little birthday rememberance.</p>
                <closer>
                <salute>Affectionately,
                Your honorary grandfather</salute>
                <signed>John N.!</signed>
                </closer>
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.36.15ab"/>
                <fw type="curatorial">15a</fw>
                
            </div1>
